[If rapid antibody tests were available for point of care use, then previously infected individuals who are not vaccinated could show proof of immunity. Even though it has been demonstrated that the vaccine boosts immunity following prior infection, and is recommended, such proof of existing immunity might be a possible compromise. - Mod.LK]

