Comparing the 7-day averages of daily confirmed cases from the past 7 days and those from 8-14 days ago, case counts have decreased by 6.5%, while daily reported deaths have decreased by 5.8%. Similar comparative 7-day averages in the USA show 17.5% decrease in daily reported cases and 6.8% decrease in reported deaths.

Impression: Worldwide over 300 000 newly confirmed infections were reported in the past 24 hours; cumulative totals of over 235.71 million cases and over 4.81 million deaths have been reported. - Mod.UBA

